The,TrainingFinder,Real,time,Affiliate,Integrated,Network,TRAIN,is,a,free,service,for,public,health,professionals,provided,by,the,Public,Health,Foundation,PHF,TRAIN,website,users,can,find,and,register,for,courses,earn,continuing,education,units,CEUs,track,their,online,learning,with,personal,transcripts,discuss,and,review,courses,and,get,notifications,on,the,latest,training,available,for,a,specified,location,or,area,of,expertise,The,TRAIN,system,can,be,integrated,with,external,learning,management,systems,LMSs,using,SOAP,based,APIs